## 📂 Variables

```hcl
variable "numbers_list" {
  type = list(number)
}

variable "obj_list" {
  type = list(object({
    city = string
    lang = string
  }))
}

variable "map_number" {
  type = map(number)
}

variable "map_string" {
  type = map(string)
}
```

